DDDslProposalProvider
public abstract class AbstractDDDslProposalProvider extends CharacterizedDataDictionaryProposalProvider
Represents a generated, default implementation of superclass CharacterizedDataDictionaryProposalProvider. Methods are dynamically dispatched on the first parameter, i.e., you can override them with a more concrete subtype.
